snippet.title: Ziggy, the Master of Thunder! (New Brawler Animation)
snippet.description:
The Great Ziggy Show starts now! 🤘

🌹 Collect 14 Ziggy Boxes during the Brawler Event to unlock him!
🪄 Get a Ziggy Box for every 2 wins
🐆 You have 3 daily tickets (which reset each day, no stacking!)
🪞 Try Ziggy for free in Mirror Matches!
✨ Ziggy will go to the Starr Road on November 6th, a few hours before the next Brawl Pass Season starts. This is a change from the previous Brawler release event and is part of testing different Brawler release setups. This likely won't change the way the Brawler release event works, since the focus is more on testing different dates and timelines throughout a season and update cycle and we will be trying a few different options in upcoming Brawler releases before committing to a specific format

Song composed and performed by Reckless Love 🎶

Kuma | Bande-annonce 01 de l’Épisode 12 (Doublé en Français)
Full Episode → https://youtu.be/AhTzM0PjGl8

Abonnez-vous aujourd’hui et plongez dans l’univers de Kuma ! → 
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCFfH8yBcEGg57loh1b07vGg?sub_confirmation=1

Après une nuit terrible, Ceylan se réveille à l’hôpital, des questions plein la tête et le cœur tourné vers Karan. Les rumeurs s’enflamment, une « pilule » pas si innocente montre son vrai visage, et les manœuvres de Sema se resserrent. Mais l’amour insiste. Karan et Ceylan tiendront-ils face aux coutumes et à la peur ? Tu paries sur qui ?

À 𝐏𝐑𝐎𝐏𝐎𝐒 𝐃𝐄 𝐊𝐔𝐌𝐀

Amour ou vengeance ? Les deux ont un prix…💔

Ceylan, une mariée en fuite, échappe à sa famille impitoyable et trouve refuge — ainsi qu’une passion électrique — dans les bras de Karan Çelikhan, héritier d’une puissante dynastie. Mais alors que leur romance secrète s’enflamme, un événement tragique fait tout basculer. Coincés entre amour et vengeance, ils doivent affronter des traditions brutales, des secrets familiaux enfouis, et un destin au lourd tribut. 

🔔 Kuma est disponible en exclusivité sur notre chaîne YouTube officielle ➤
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCFfH8yBcEGg57loh1b07vGg?sub_confirmation=1

Portée par Aybüke Yılmaz et Emre Özmen, cette série met en scène un duel bouleversant entre amour, haine et destin. Grâce à son rythme haletant et son intrigue percutante, Kuma captivera les spectateurs semaine après semaine.

≫ Produite par Stellar Yapım, GoQuest Media & VIP 2000
≫ Créatrice de la série : İnci Gülen Oarr
≫ Réalisation : Atilla Cengiz & Irmak Çengel
≫ Directeurs de la photographie : Sinan Onur & Ferhat Özyurt
≫ Musique : Saki Cimen
≫ Scénario : Ahmet Köseoğlu & Gökçen Eroğlu

𝐃𝐢𝐬𝐭𝐫𝐢𝐛𝐮𝐭𝐢𝐨𝐧 𝐩𝐫𝐢𝐧𝐜𝐢𝐩𝐚𝐥𝐞:

Emre Özmen dans le rôle de Karan (rôle principal masculin)
Aybüke Yılmaz dans le rôle de Ceylan (rôle principal féminin)
Hilal Tüfek dans le rôle de Sema (épouse de Salih, belle-sœur de Karan)
Ufuk Kaplan dans le rôle de Kudret Çelikhan (mère de Karan et Salih) 

𝐃𝐢𝐬𝐭𝐫𝐢𝐛𝐮𝐭𝐢𝐨𝐧 𝐒𝐞𝐜𝐨𝐧𝐝𝐚𝐢𝐫𝐞:

≫ Sezgin Irmak dans le rôle de Salih Çelikhan (frère aîné de Karan)
≫ Ayça Bilir dans le rôle de Aliye Olcay Çelikhan (fille de Salih et Meltem)
≫ Burak Özen dans le rôle de Emir Çelikhan (enfant adoptif d’Hikmet)
≫ Ayşegül Şen dans le rôle de Meltem Olcay (liaison secrète de Salih)

𝙲𝚑𝚊𝚗𝚗𝚎𝚕 𝚖𝚊𝚗𝚊𝚐𝚎𝚍 𝚋𝚢 𝚃𝚞𝚛𝚗𝚒𝚗𝚐 𝚁𝚎𝚍 𝙼𝚎𝚍𝚒𝚊𝚌𝚘𝚛𝚙 𝚘𝚗 𝚋𝚎𝚑𝚊𝚕𝚏 𝚘𝚏 𝙶𝚘𝚚𝚞𝚎𝚜𝚝 𝙼𝚎𝚍𝚒𝚊 𝚞𝚗𝚍𝚎𝚛 𝚘𝚞𝚛 “𝚈𝚘𝚞𝚃𝚞𝚋𝚎 𝙵𝚒𝚛𝚜𝚝” 𝚒𝚗𝚒𝚝𝚒𝚊𝚝𝚒𝚟𝚎.

snippet.title: JUJUTSU KAISEN: Execution - Official Teaser Trailer (English Subtitles)
snippet.description:
The best of the Shibuya Incident arc combines with the debut of the first two episodes of Season 3's Culling Game arc in this exclusive theatrical event! Coming to North America exclusively in movie theatres starting December 5.

A veil abruptly descends over the busy Shibuya area amid the bustling Halloween crowds, trapping countless civilians inside. Satoru Gojo, the strongest jujutsu sorcerer, steps into the chaos. But lying in wait are curse users and spirits scheming to seal him away.
Yuji Itadori, accompanied by his classmates and other top-tier jujutsu sorcerers, enters the fray in an unprecedented clash of curses — the Shibuya Incident.
In the aftermath, ten colonies across Japan are transformed into dens of curses in a plan orchestrated by Noritoshi Kamo, the most wicked sorcerer in history. As the deadly Culling Game starts, Special Grade sorcerer Yuta Okkotsu is assigned to carry out Yuji’s execution for his perceived crimes.
The desperate confrontation between Satoru Gojo’s two beloved students comes to the big screen with an early preview. Be the first to experience Yuji and Yuta’s fateful battle with the hotly anticipated kickoff to Season 3 in theatres nationwide.

#IGN #Anime

A veil abruptly descends over the busy Shibuya area amid the bustling Halloween crowds, trapping countless civilians inside. Satoru Gojo, the strongest jujutsu sorcerer, steps into the chaos. But lying in wait are curse users and spirits scheming to seal him away.
Yuji Itadori, accompanied by his classmates and other top-tier jujutsu sorcerers, enters the fray in an unprecedented clash of curses — the Shibuya Incident.
In the aftermath, ten colonies across Japan are transformed into dens of curses in a plan orchestrated by Noritoshi Kamo, the most wicked sorcerer in history. As the deadly Culling Game starts, Special Grade sorcerer Yuta Okkotsu is assigned to carry out Yuji’s execution for his perceived crimes.
The desperate confrontation between Satoru Gojo’s two beloved students comes to the big screen with an early preview. Be the first to experience Yuji and Yuta’s fateful battle with the hotly anticipated kickoff to Season 3 in theatres nationwide.

#IGN #Anime
